column90:
GROVER, Mr. JONATHAN R 
Member ID:  09384 
Member Type:  Attorney 
License Status:  Active 
Firm:  Evans Grover & Beins PC 
Phone:  (435)257-6590 
Law School:  Thomas Jefferson School of Law 
Graduated:  2001 
Bar Admission:  05/15/2002

Jonathan R. Grover was born in Logan, Utah in 1974. He received a Bachelor of Science Degree in Prelaw, with a minor in Philosophy and a Liberal Arts and Sciences Certificate from Utah State University in 1997. He received his Juris Doctor Degree from Thomas Jefferson School of Law, San Diego, California in 2001. He is admitted to practice before all courts in Utah, California and Idaho, as well as the United States District Court for the Districts of Utah, Idaho and Central District of California. Jonathan is a member of the Box Elder County Bar Association. 

Jonathan has worked for the Law Offices of Anh Viet Pham in Westminster, California, as well as Olson & Hoggan, P.C. in Logan, Utah. Jonathan begin a solo practice in 2003 before forming and becoming a partner with Evans, Grover & Beins, P.C. Areas of practice include: Agriculture, Business Litigation, Criminal Defense, Divorce, Family Law, Personal Injury, Insurance, Real Estate, and Trusts, Wills and Estate Planning. 

Jonathan is married with 3 children. He enjoys spending time with his family, snowmobiling, waterskiing, reading, farming and gardening.
